Project Proposal:
——————————————————————————————————————————
A document that defines the purpose of the project and the anticipated business value to justify proceeding with said project.

Sections:
	1. problem statement
		-one to five sentences that defines what the problem is
		-should be at the top of the document

	2. project delvierables and value
		-details what is the output and value 

	3. key stakeholders
		-who to contact for questions

	4. project timeline

	5. budget

	6. additional notes
		-catch all for anything that didnt fit in any other section

	7. approval signatures
		-people who will provide the budget and oversee the project 
——————————————————————————————————————————